<br>
Simple solution really...  Mob X has guild A, B, C, D wanting to kill it.  It's supposed to pop on say monday...  It's currently Guild B's turn.  They attempt it say... twice, die each time.  Guild C comes in, kills the mob.  Now he's shedualed to pop next monday, and now it's guild D's turn.<br>
