<br>
I would be in favor of more quests that use tradeskills and triggered spawns.  In example: The coldain ring and prayer shawl quests, the ethereal bladed naginata, etc.<br>
<br>
If Verant could implement more quests of this sort, it might solve the problem.  However if they keep with their current pattern of forcing players to kill named, random spawn mobs (i.e. Woushi, Lodizal, etc) we are back to square one.<br>
<br>
