<br>
So not only can one guild go in there and start at noon before any other guild is done with work etc, they can do it in around 6 hours, and then have the rest of the week to kill whatever else they want. <br>
<br>
The best thing Verant could do is to randomize the spawns in NToV. Make a few of the mobs spawn each day, preferably ones in different sections of North, and you solve parts of the bottleneck problem that you have with one guild killing everything. If they wanted every mob in North, they would have to spend a decent amount of time there each day, taking them out of the picture on some of the other mobs that spawn later in the week and spreading the wealth a little, so to speak. <br>
<br>
This will never happen though, as we all know Uberguilds are Verant's baby and they like to take care of them. They constantly cater to those that are in an area first and ignore the general public's needs and wishes. <p><b>Xantheus Diabolus</b></a><BR>
